EDDIE IZZARD - SEXIE (2003) (MKV)

Through Australia, New Zealand, Canada, USA, Ireland and the
UK, this tour was performed to more people than there are
in Iceland (280,000).

Filmed in Eastbourne where his grandfather and father were
born and where he went to school, this show is the funniest
live show that could ever be performed by a warm blooded
animal.
